data.description: **This COULD be your FOREVER RETIREMENT Home. Little maintenance required so you have more time for living with a smaller lot and NEW BUILT HOME.**  Are you still looking for your DREAM HOME?  *Virtually Staged* Welcome to your DREAM HOME with an incredible opportunity! This stunning property offers MORE UPGRADES than the builder is offering, making THIS the perfect time to make this FULLY upgraded HOME yours to OWN just in time for the Holidays.    This custom 1-story, 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home ALMOST 2300 sq ft of living space is ready to welcome you and your family. Boasting over $50,000+ in builder upgrades and more. The kitchen has a butler area that extends the kitchen space- great for entertaining extended layout of cabinets and counters, creates an ideal setting for entertaining family and friends.     An upgraded additional window in the kitchen area makes this even more brighter. Extended and Upgraded granite counter and backsplash, stainless steel kitchen and laundry room sinks, including a paid solar system, 2 additional windows in the master bedroom making this a brighter and airy space, and shutters throughout.     As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living room, thoughtfully wired for an amazing sound system – perfect  for setting the ambiance or hosting movie nights with loved ones. The elegance of window shutters and patio shutter doors can be found  throughout this single-story gem.    The right side of the property leads you to the bedrooms, bathrooms, and a conveniently upgraded laundry room with stainless steel sink, enhancing daily living convenience. The left side of the home presents the master ensuite, enhanced with additional windows that infuse the room with a bright and airy feel. The generously sized rooms throughout the home offers ample space for your growing family and guests.    This property is tailor-made for hosting unforgettable gatherings, especially during the Holiday season. Reach out now to schedule an appointment to see this exceptional home, or inquire about assuming this loan with its remarkable interest rate.    Step outside to the covered California Patio area, complete with overhead lights and pre-wired for fans, overlooking the manageable  backyard – the perfect space for everyday family living and entertaining. This home has it all and is ready to become your  forever haven. Don't wait; it won't last long!
